reviewText: This DVD plays only on my DVD car deck and my computer. It DOES NOT play on the home DVD player nor the Blu Ray Player. If it did I would give it 5 stars. Donna's performance is great. The audio is also very good.
I have reviewed this recording before on copy that would pay on my dvd player and it was a good performance but the copy that I received would not play on my dvd player

WHEN I FIRST LISTENED THIS CONCERTE MANY YEARS AGO,I REMEMBER THOSE DISCO DAYS.
WHAT A WONDERFUL PERFOMANCE OF THIS LADY AND I HAVE MANY MEMORIES OF THAT TIME.
DONNA IS AT HER PEAK OF HER VOCAL TALENT.A GREAT SINGER. ONE OF THE BEST THAT USA GIVES TO THE WORLD
